      • wrap

        public static AnimatorProxy wrap(View view)
        Create a proxy to allow for modifying post-3.0 view properties on all pre-3.0 platforms. DO NOT wrap your views if you are using ObjectAnimator as it will handle that itself.
        Parameters:
        view - View to wrap.
        Returns:
        Proxy to post-3.0 properties.
